# su/ — Visual Logic Canvas
# format: ctx/1.0
# last-verified: 2026-03-27
# edges: -> call/render | ~> subscribe/read | => HTTP API call

## Components
  SUShell : Main canvas: 97 voice functions, 12 object renderers, Play/Pause, tutorials, config panels [root] @entry
    -> LogicEditor, ColorPicker
    ~> labStore, gameVoiceStore, logicEngine, behaviorSync, recipeRunner, recipes, ariaEngine, trainingLogger
    => termuxRouter, gameRouter
  LogicEditor : Full-screen node editor: wire drawing, block config, typed port system [component]
    ~> labStore, logicEngine
  ColorPicker : Hue slider + 8 presets [component]

## State Stores
  labStore : 12 objects, LogicGraph, playMode, undo, presets [store]
  gameVoiceStore : Aria orb state (useGameVoiceStore @ store/gameVoice) [store]

## Libraries
  logicEngine : executeFromSource, evaluateBlock (8 types) [lib]
  behaviorSync : Card-Graph sync [lib]
  recipeRunner : Tutorial step execution [lib]
  recipes : 5 tutorials [lib]
  ariaEngine : Voice AI connection [lib]
  trainingLogger : Dataset capture [lib]

## Backend
  termuxRouter : Termux device API — torch, battery, notification, volume, camera/photo, dynamic bc.targetLabel [backend]
  gameRouter : Game API — /api/game/voice-config (Aria engine key + config) [backend]
